  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    UICore
    UICore is the base of all UIElemetns and Interactions with the computer.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Board  
    Card
    Abstract class for all cards
    Controller
    Class for running the game, includes main function
    Country
    Class for Country objects on the map
    Debug
    Container for all debugging tools
    Deck
    Class holding the deck of cards.
    Effects
    Container for all effects for all cards
    Player  
    ScoringCard
    Extends Card and implements Comparable.
    TurnCard
    Turn Card extends Card and implements Comparable
    UIGraphic
    UIGraphic is a implementation of UICore that will have a graphical interface an allow for a more traditonal windows interface.
    UIText
    UI implementation solely based on command prompt
    UnitTests  
  • Enum Summary
